social_posts.post_text: Alone time in our family🙄

We had so much fun during this Christmas family photoshoot with @kristijophotography 

I know that all photographers have their own styles but this photographer took our session to a whole another level. She had such realistic Santa waiting for us. Santa knew my kids names, had real sugar cookies for them, showed them their names on his Nice list and even gave them deer food to go before we left. I mean... I was blown away. It was definitely Christmas magic unlike anything we experienced before🎄

I'll be posting more from our family shoot within the next few days and I'll post Kristi's website in my stories. If you are in Riverside county and looking for an amazing photographer, look no further ❤️
Aurora is clearly enjoying her first meeting with Santa during our Christmas photoshoot with @kristijophotography
Christmas vibes😁

Merry Christmas, everyone! I hope you had an amazing celebration with your loved ones...🎄❤

P.S. Photos by amazing @kristijophotography
